UBS Chairman Says Basel III Tougher Than Seems, Le Temps Reports

-- B y   W a r r e n   G i l e s
-- 
2011-02-24T07:32:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-24/ubs-chairman-says-basel-iii-tougher-than-seems-le-temps-reports.html
  UBS AG  Chairman Kaspar Villiger said
the Basel III regulations are “tougher than they appear,”  Le
Temps  reported, citing a meeting with Swiss newspapers.  Villiger, 70, declined to talk about a successor, the
Geneva-based newspaper said, adding that the implementation of
the bank’s strategy isn’t complete.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Warren Giles in Geneva at 
 wgiles@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at 
 fconnelly@bloomberg.net  